values: well another turkey day has come and gone! And this year for some reason i didnt get depressed!! must be the magic pills im taking. yay. anyways i had dinner at grampys and of course it was delicious, then i helped mom with the dishes, dev went to ryans and mom and i took a nap then went and saw timeline. it was a horrible movie. :( too bad. oh well i like hangin out with mum and now i dont have to see it with erik, thank god. Then i went over to janelles and we went to harb for hot coco. mmm. they put whipped cream on it though, ick. im thankful for my life right now, its happy and im happy for the most part and i have a job. yay! at cafe ruba!! mmm mochas!!! well i dont know if im going to go out again tonight , we will see :)

from a movie with erik. The elf is really cute and funny. I laughed outloud a few times  :) i got gloves tonight, two pairs for 1.50!!! so goood!! yay. i dunno what to write right now. more later then.

by not going to english, but im so tired and that would require sooo much time and effort. Id rather just work a little harder and do a few extre credits to make up for it. 

So life has been pretty okay lately. Those pills the doc gave me make me really happy and i just went back and he upped the dose. Gotta love doctors :)

Boys.. are the same as always, the only difference is that right now i really dont care. Aj is really needy which is annoying haha. 
Joel is joel, im going to a movie with mike this weekend (if all goes well), steve.. is well... new subject. 

School sucks. I totally got my ass kicked by a test in biz law today. Speech will be okay i think. I got an A on the only test we've had and i participate enough so.. my only reaal concern is english.. well maybe biz law too. haha. I just need to kick it up a notch. 

J is out of the hospital. She says it was horrible and i can just imagine. I hope we can succeed in making her feel less lonely. 

My mom is being nice i guess. She is always on my ass about school and stuff. 

I had another interview at Ruba but he told me to call him if he doesnt call me within a few days so im going to call him tomorrow, because it will have been 3 days since the interview. My phone is ringing and if its ryan im gunna be pissed. He wants me to go to some thing in corona and hes been trying to get me to go for weeks!!!

It wasnt him. It was J! and we are going to the block. :) 

So ya. things are looking up. There is a bright side to every.. tunnel. Or something. I dont remember how that saying goes. My memory is shot to hell. haha. im hungry.

its been a long weekend. I get to go curl up in a little ball in my bed and fake sleep now. Everything is just so complicated.. my mind wont shutup long enough for me to fall asleep. I cant help picturing her in whats sure to be a stark white room with a metal railed bed.. and the girl next to her babbling. Shes bound to be crying and wishing things were different, but she cant take it back now, and i kept telling her that.. what do you want to happen now? What was the point? But she doesnt have an answer. I completely get her and i think she knows that, but i wish i could do more.. but what can i really do? This is her battle.. and she has to want to win. 
Gosh now AJ broke up with A... crap. i dunno what to do.. its not my fault though, they were having problems before whatever happened happened. Joel is being disgusting. ew. the thought of someone smelling my shorts makes me sick. Why do guys do that? Noodle and i were talking about that the other day. wierd freaks, id never try to smell a guys shorts!!!

I went to the doctors yesterday and talked to him about stuff. He was new so ive never had him before, but he talked to me ALOT which was annoying, but it was nice that someone actually cares about me, even if he is paid to. He seemed to keep talking in circles, and more for his own enjoyment, but oh well. Talking is nice.  I dont know how this whole cafe ruba thing is going to work out. The girl really liked me, but i dunno about the guy. I guess i will know my tomorrow, but my hair isnt acceptable or something. Tooo bad, im a package. I dont come without my hair lol. Tonight was stupid. I had a feeling that nhu would hang out with chris instead of going to the movie so i wasnt to annoyed when it actually happened. I wish he wasnt such an ass to her. We are all so stupid, we follow guys around like little puppy dogs batting our fucking eye lashes hoping to catch their attention, even if only for a second. Then we cry when they walk right by us... and start the whole pattern over again. I wish that for once we could like someone and have them like us back on the same level. Is that ever possible? I doubt it, not as far as ive seen at least, but then again i prefer to keep my eyes closed to the whole business. Its 10:09 on a friday night and i dont even give a fuck that im home. I think i am going to start staying home more and hopefully i will get this job and that will occupy my time. I just need to make sense of things and find my place among all of this chaos. As noodle said this has been a trying week, although i dont think anyone is taking it seriously enough, but its not my family so what can i do? I shouldnt talk though, my family kind of tends to "forget" when i fuck up.. no one wants to face the ugly things in life. No one wants to stand up to the truth and realize that they may need some help or may to need to step up and help someone else for a change. My doc. says i need to be less selfish and try to think about what other people are going through and how they feel to. thats good advice, but first i need to figure out how i feel. I feel positive for the first time. Im going to take a hot bath and read, and then maybe i will write some more, or go to sleep.

just got back from harb. i wanted to go to cafe ruba but J didnt want to. I cant call him J cuz that is a diff code name.. oh well. I dunno what else to put im not feeling creative. erik is asking me right now to go to a movie with him on friday. i dont think this would be a good idea seeing as he told aj that he likes me. arg. well im going to go to the doctors tomorrow. im sick of being this sad. id rather be artificially happy than not happy at all and im fucking sick of people asking me whats wrong. i doubt ill be able to get an appointment and then the weekend will come and i will be fucking trapped. "It's hard for me to smile when I am hurting. It's hard for me to talk when you won't understand. It's hard for me to reach out when I need help the most." school is looking bad, i need to work harder if i want to get the fuck out of this stupid town. away from all of these fake people. i have no clothes and i havent been shopping in forever. weeks i think. ya weeks for sure. oh well, it doesnt even make me happy anymore.
i may have done some thing kind of shady :( But i dont feel that bad, and that is what sucks. Oh well , not my fault. well partly.

so steve just IMed me and apologized for being a complete ass. he said that he really liked me and i was a challenge so he got frustrated and blew up. That was kinda nice i guess. Hes like call me sometime or IM me, and im like "i deleted your SN and number". i think he got mad. Then he waited a few minutes and IM'ed me again saying that he wanted to see me , so to call him, and he gave me his number. I told him that i will probably not call for a while cuz im wierd lately. He didnt understand. i didnt expect him to. To much went on today to writa all about it. Very emotional. Trang is going to be in my prayers big time. She is very lucky to have brian by her side. I know that if i went through something like what she is going through i wouldnt have anyone there for me. im going to take a hot bath now.
I needed someone to talk to so i called joel, i dont know why i did that. it was stupid, he had to get off the phone anyway. im going to leaveee now.

This is a cute picture. the good old days.. like last month. haha!! Umm.. i just wrote soo much and it deleted it. oh well, lifes a bitch and then you die.
